\c 17
\nb
\v 1 Ungahlabeli iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho inkabi kumbe imvu okukuyo isici, loba yiyiphi into embi, ngoba kuyisinengiso eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wakho\x + Levi 22.20.\x*.
\p
\v 2 Uba kutholakala phakathi kwakho, loba phakathi kwaliphi lamasango akho, iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekunika wona, owesilisa loba owesifazana owenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho\x + 17.7. 13.6-14.\x*, ngokweqa isivumelwano sayo\x + Josh. 7.11,15. 23.16. Hlu. 2.20. 2 Kho. 18.12. Hos. 6.7. 8.1.\x*,
\v 3 abesesiyakhonza abanye onkulunkulu, abakhothamele, loba ilanga kumbe inyanga, kumbe enye yebutho lamazulu\x + 4.19.\x*, engingakulayanga\x + Jer. 7.31. 19.5. 32.35.\x*,
\v 4 ube usukubikelwa, ukuzwe, uzakubuzisisa, khangela-ke, kuliqiniso, indaba iqinisekile, lesosinengiso senziwe koIsrayeli\x + 13.14.\x*,
\v 5 uzayikhupha leyondoda kumbe lowo owesifazana, abenze leyonto embi, emasangweni akho, leyondoda kumbe lowo owesifazana, ubakhande ngamatshe baze bafe\x + Levi 24.14,16. Josh. 7.25.\x*.
\v 6 Ngomlomo wabafakazi ababili loba wabafakazi abathathu ofanele ukufa uzabulawa; kayikubulawa ngomlomo womfakazi oyedwa\x + Nani 35.30. Joha. 8.17.\x*.
\v 7 Isandla sabafakazi sizakuba ngesokuqala phezu kwakhe ukumbulala, lemva kwalokho isandla sabo bonke abantu\x + 13.9; Seb. 7.58.\x*. Ngalokhu uzakhupha ububi phakathi kwakho\x + 17.12. 13.5.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Uba kulodaba olulukhuni kakhulu kuwe ekwahluleleni\x + 19.17. 21.5. 2 Lan. 19.8,10. Hlab. 122.5. Jer. 18.18. Hag. 2.11. Mal. 2.7.\x*, phakathi kwegazi legazi, phakathi kwesahlulelo lesahlulelo, laphakathi kokutshaya lokutshaya, indaba zokuphikisana emasangweni akho, khona uzasukuma\x + 19.17. 21.5. 2 Lan. 19.8,10. Hlab. 122.5. Jer. 18.18. Hag. 2.11. Mal. 2.7.\x* uye endaweni iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ezayikhetha\x + 12.5.\x*,
\v 9 uze kubapristi abangamaLevi\x + 19.17. 21.5. 2 Lan. 19.8,10. Hlab. 122.5. Jer. 18.18. Hag. 2.11. Mal. 2.7.\x* lakumahluleli ozakuba ekhona ngalezonsuku, uzabuza\x + 19.17. 21.5. 2 Lan. 19.8,10. Hlab. 122.5. Jer. 18.18. Hag. 2.11. Mal. 2.7.\x*; babesebekutshela isinqumo sesahlulelo\x + Hez. 44.24.\x*.
\v 10 Njalo uzakwenza njengokwesinqumo abazakutshela sona kuleyondawo iN\nd kosi\nd* ezayikhetha; njalo unanzelele ukwenza njengakho konke abazakufundisa khona.
\v 11 Njengokomthetho abazakufundisa wona, lanjengokwesahlulelo abazakutshela sona, uzakwenza. Kawuyikuphambuka kusinqumo abazakutshela sona, uye ngakwesokunene kumbe ngakwesokhohlo.
\v 12 Lendoda eyenza ngokuziqhenya ukuze ingalaleli umpristi\x + 17.13. Dute. 1.43. 18.20,22. Ezra 10.8.\x* omi ukukhonza khona iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho\x + 10.8. 18.5,7.\x*, kumbe umahluleli, leyondoda izakufa. Ngalokhu uzakhupha ububi koIsrayeli\x + 13.5.\x*.
\v 13 Njalo bonke abantu bazakuzwa, besabe, bangaphindi ukuziqhenya\x + 13.11.\x*.
\s Imilayezo ngenkosi
\p
\v 14 Lapho usufikile elizweni iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekunika lona ukuthi udle ilifa lalo, uhlale kilo, ubususithi: Ngizazimisela inkosi njengazo zonke izizwe ezingizingelezeleyo\x + 1 Sam. 8.5,19,20.\x*;
\v 15 umbeke lokumbeka abe yinkosi phezu kwakho, yena iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ezamkhetha\x + 1 Sam. 9.15. 10.24. 16.12. 1 Lan. 22.10.\x*. Evela phakathi kwabafowenu umbeke abe yinkosi phezu kwakho\x + Jer. 30.21.\x*; kawulakumbeka owezizweni phezu kwakho ongesumfowenu.
\v 16 Kodwa angazandiseli amabhiza\x + 1 Kho. 4.26. 10.26,28. 2 Lan. 1.16. 9.28.\x*, njalo angababuyiseli abantu eGibhithe ukuze andise amabhiza\x + Isa. 31.1. Hez. 17.15.\x*, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* ithe kini: Kalisayikubuyela futhi ngaleyondlela\x + 28.68; Hos. 11.5; Eks. 13.17; Nani 14.3,4; Jer. 42.15-19.\x*.
\v 17 Futhi angazandiseli abafazi, ukuze inhliziyo yakhe ingaphambuki; njalo angazandiseli kakhulu isiliva legolide\x + 1 Kho. 11.3,4.\x*.
\v 18 Kuzakuthi esehlala esihlalweni sobukhosi sombuso wakhe, uzazibhalela impinda yalumlayo egwalweni\x + 2 Kho. 11.12.\x*, okuvela \add kulokho\add* okuphambi\x + 31.9,26. 2 Kho. 22.8. 2 Lan. 34.14.\x* kwabapristi abangamaLevi\x + 17.9. Dute. 18.1. 24.8. 27.9. Josh. 3.3. 8.33.\x*.
\v 19 Njalo luzakuba laye, njalo abale kulo insuku zonke zempilo yakhe\x + Josh. 1.8.\x*, ukuze afunde ukuyesaba iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakhe, agcine wonke amazwi alumlayo lezimiso lezi, akwenze\x + 4.10; 14.23.\x*,
\v 20 ukuze inhliziyo yakhe ingaziphakamisi phezu kwabafowabo, lokuze angaphambuki emthethweni \add aye\add* ngakwesokunene loba ngakwesokhohlo\x + 5.32. 1 Kho. 15.5.\x*, ukuze elule izinsuku embusweni wakhe, yena labantwana bakhe, phakathi kukaIsrayeli\x + 4.40.\x*.
